>"},{"pid":"77329788283f319fa39a9ed3d980e55f720c8cd1","tid":183704,"uid":59400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T16:37:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>大狗定細狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我養大狗試過一舊豬骨呑落肚 擔心左我幾日最後又無事<br />\n不過你個舊係膠一定要睇下佢聽日有無痾返出黎<br />\n如果無而且直情無大便好可能係塞住左要睇醫生<br />\n希望佢無事啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n細狗黎，係咁等緊佢痾，好擔心，望住佢仲傻下傻下既樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}